com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.event.Observable
public class DmdGridStore
extends com.extjs.gxt.ui.client.store.ListStore<DmoExtGWTWrapperBase<DmcObject>>

The DmdGridStore provides the backing store for a DmdGrid. The objects stored are generated wrapper objects derived from DmoExtGWTWrapperBase and should implement the DmcNamedObjectIF interface. This allows for easy deletion of named objects from the store.

peter
